Embedded fonts — licensing
===========================

text_shaper.wasm embeds a 3-family × 4-style matrix (12 faces). Font id
= family base (0 sans / 4 serif / 8 mono) + (bold?1:0) + (italic?2:0).

Sans + Mono — Apache License 2.0
  (http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0):
- Roboto-Regular / -Bold / -Italic / -BoldItalic.ttf
    © Google (Christian Robertson)
- RobotoMono-Regular / -Bold / -Italic / -BoldItalic.ttf
    © The Roboto Mono Project Authors

Serif — SIL Open Font License 1.1 (https://scripts.sil.org/OFL):
- PTSerif-Regular / -Bold / -Italic / -BoldItalic.ttf
    © ParaType Inc. (PT Serif)

Both licenses permit embedding and redistribution (including inside a
compiled WebAssembly binary) provided the license + attribution are
retained — which this file does.

Sources:
- https://github.com/googlefonts/roboto
- https://github.com/googlefonts/RobotoMono
- https://github.com/google/fonts/tree/main/ofl/ptserif
